# Zero Trust Architecture Infographic

## Purpose

This infographic explains Zero Trust Architecture as a security model based on continuous verification, least privilege, and assuming threats may already exist inside the environment.

## Concepts Covered

- Verify explicitly
- Least privilege access
- Assume breach
- Network segmentation
- Identity-based access
- Continuous monitoring

## Why This Matters in Security Operations

Zero Trust helps security teams reduce risk by limiting trust, monitoring access, and making it harder for attackers to move laterally through an environment.

